---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About the Desk" description="About UK IHT Desk">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-primary mb-8">About the Desk</h1>
    <div class="font-body text-ink leading-relaxed">
      <p>UK 继承税与遗产规划（IHT / probate / 跨境遗产 / nil rate band 实操）</p>
      <p class="mt-4">This is an independent editorial site. We are not affiliated with any institution mentioned unless explicitly disclosed. Content is researched and written for informational purposes.</p>
      <p class="mt-4">Contact: <code>contact@ukinheritance.com</code></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>